Design, own & implement the strategy to recruit key/top-potential candidates at a high volume and fast pace, for a wide variety of programs ranging from Apprenticeship to POEC, maintaining a successful offer acceptance rate with the ability to also build sourcing capabilities in collaboration with the students growth team;
Review, screen and engage with sourced candidates, assess and evaluate their profile, interview them and close candidates, assisting the Matching team in matching effectively candidates to the best possible offering;
