Build and automate as much as possible the admissions processes to function at scale without adding extra human labour;
Manage, coach and grow a team across international markets, set up process discipline, improve ways of working and define goals & priorities;
Report on your team’s performance (revenues, gross margin, etc.) and ensure proper allocation of efforts.
Requirements
