HR leader with a strong domain knowledge and expertise in talent acquisition and candidate search and hiring;
Strategy leader with excellent verbal and written communication skills;
Demonstrated hands-on experience and ready to build a team and processes almost from scratch at a fast pace;
Strong track record of solving complex problems, designing creative strategies, and delivering significant impact;
Strong analytical skills and comfortable playing with numbers, drawing key insights from analytics to make the application hiring process smarter and more efficient;
Ability to define, document, standardize processes, share with the team and finally source tools to automate efforts;
Deep interest in technology and experience working in cross-functional environment along with growth marketing, data analysts & PMs;
Experience hiring, mentoring, coaching & retaining a high-performing team (10+), exhibiting poise & dynamism to motivate and spread confidence.

